@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1 class="display-4 mb-5">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        1. Introduction
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>Welcome to MyBookStore. This is a test project, which means no real data is used, stored, or shared. However, for the purpose of simulating a real-world application, we have provided this privacy policy.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        2. Information We Collect
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>Since this is a test project, we do not actually collect any real user data. Any data you enter is for testing purposes only and should not be considered secure.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        3. How We Use Information
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>Any information entered into [Your Test Project Name] is purely for simulation and testing purposes. No real-world actions are taken based on this data.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        4. Sharing Your Information
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>We do not share any data from this test project with third parties, as the data is fictional and for testing purposes only.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        5. Data Security
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>While we aim to protect the fictional data in this project, please note that no real data should be entered and no data entered should be considered secure.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        6. Your Rights
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>As this is a test project, there are no real user rights associated with your data. However, in a real-world scenario, users would have rights to access, edit, and delete their personal data.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time, but since this is a test project, changes will be for testing purposes only.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header">
        8. Contact Us
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>For any questions about this test project's privacy policy, you can contact us at vikito11111@gmail.com.</p>
    </div>
</div>
